						<div class="postbody">On a technical note, nes_ntsc 0.1.7 is ~41% faster than the C/C++ version of HQ2X.  I'd say it's fairly well optimized. :p
<br />
<br />Edit: Oh, and that's even with the very slow interpolated (instead of simply duplicated) scanline doubling in my implementation!
<br />
<br />- randi</div>

					
